= Pure Ruby PostgreSQL interface

This is a library to access PostgreSQL (>= 7.4) from Ruby without the need of
any C library.

This is a maintained fork designed to address unfixed problems in the main
repository, with a goal of proper functioning with Sequel's postgres adapter.

